[SPEAKER_04] mislim oni pokazuju već i svojom pojavnošću,

584
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:33,200
[SPEAKER_04] svojom pojavnošću pokazuju da su ipak sad woman friendly,

585
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,940
[SPEAKER_04] jel nose haljinu, pa ja ću poznati tva Ivana Lovrića.

586
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:40,599
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da na kavu i berat ću se.

587
00:30:40,599 --> 00:30:42,359
[SPEAKER_02] Ajde, Lovrića ti do haljini.

588
00:30:42,599 --> 00:30:43,740
[SPEAKER_02] Doprinjeće ovoj temi, aj.

589
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,500
[SPEAKER_02] Moćeš jednu spesa, ali još?

590
00:30:45,500 --> 00:30:46,720
[SPEAKER_01] Aj, još jedna haljina ide.

591
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:47,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ajde haljina.

592
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:48,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ajde haljina.

593
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da, gledaj, ovaj, Stanko je pito ili ti što je s katoličkom crkvom.

594
00:30:56,700 --> 00:31:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Katolička crkva je, u tom smislu, nije sasvim ispano reći ljudska institucija,

595
00:31:05,119 --> 00:31:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] jer to je onda opet potrebno interpretira što to je.

596
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je i ljudska.

597
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je institucija krcata ljudima.

598
00:31:12,599 --> 00:31:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] I ako govorimo o ovoj putovićoj crkvi na zemlji,

599
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] bojujućoj, tako zvanoj,

600
00:31:17,619 --> 00:31:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] ona je u tom smislu institucija koju čine ljudi koji su od krvi i mesa.

601
00:31:25,339 --> 00:31:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da nju ne treba braniti tamo gdje ju ne treba braniti.

602
00:31:31,059 --> 00:31:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu, ako se može jasno pokazati mizogine obrazce,

603
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:40,039
