632
00:33:12,700 --> 00:33:14,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, Sveti Augustin, koliko god bio veliki,

633
00:33:14,819 --> 00:33:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] je u krivu, to ona kaže.

634
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:20,539
