638
00:33:27,180 --> 00:33:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] Plus što tekst jasno ukazuje,

639
00:33:29,660 --> 00:33:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] kad ga čitaš pozorno,

640
00:33:30,900 --> 00:33:32,660
[SPEAKER_00] da postoji uzlazna linija stvaranja,

641
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:34,660
[SPEAKER_00] od nežive materije preko živih bića

642
00:33:34,660 --> 00:33:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] do na kraju čovjeka koje je stvoren na kraju,

643
00:33:36,900 --> 00:33:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali pisac očito ima potrebu

644
00:33:38,900 --> 00:33:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] naglasiti različitost startnih pozicija.

645
00:33:41,619 --> 00:33:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] Adam je stvoren iz blata,

646
00:33:43,579 --> 00:33:45,339
