649
00:33:48,059 --> 00:33:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] Adam je uveden u vrt,

650
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] spustio je tvrd san,

651
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:52,039
