656
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, pisac sto,

657
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] ja tako nestručnjak,

658
00:34:02,079 --> 00:34:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] totalni lajk u tim stvarima,

659
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:04,839
[SPEAKER_00] mogu zaključiti da očigledno

660
00:34:04,839 --> 00:34:05,839
